com.shearosario.tothepathandback

Class Station

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shearosario.tothepathandback.Station

  • public class Station
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    shea A class representing a station in the PATH system.

    Included in each station is its name, unique ID, city and state, and its latitude and longitude. The location given in the station is not an entrance, but rather the given location reported by the Port Authority and Google Maps. In addition, each station includes a Entrance ArrayList holding all the entrances to that station. These entrances are obtained from an imported database.
